    "longBusinessSummary": "Dar AlBalad for Business Solutions Company provides information technology (IT) consulting services and solutions. The company's services include continuous monitoring, maintenance, troubleshooting, and support, ensuring a seamless and efficient digital environment, such as end-user support services, service desk services, application support services, and infrastructure support services. It also offers business-managed services, such as supply chain management, administrative management, and logistics management. Additionally, it offers Internet of Things (IoT) device supply, installation, and management solutions. It serves technology and telecommunications, insurance and healthcare, government and utilities, and financial industries. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia. Dar AlBalad for Business Solutions Company operates as a subsidiary of Dar AlBalad Commercial Company.",
